data.description: Standing Strong and waiting for you is this 4 bedroom, 1 bath, brick home. Inviting front porch welcomes you to relax in its privacy. Through the front door you will find the cozy living room with newer carpeting, which flows into the dining room featuring original hardwood floors. Bright kitchen with appliances included and access to the porch and concrete patio area. One bedroom is on the main floor and upstairs you will find a quaint landing area and the other 3 bedrooms boasting hardwood floors keeping with the charm of the era. Some updated wiring and added insulation, low maintenance yard, 200 amp service and one car garage complete your new home! Zoned DMU.
